    {
      "id": "sybil_24_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_24",
      "description": "This AP2-generation roadster is a masterclass in high-revving precision. Powered by the legendary F22C1 naturally aspirated inline-four, the VTEC engagement remains sharp and visceral. The drivetrain features a close-ratio six-speed manual transmission paired with a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Built on a rigid X-bone monocoque chassis with four-wheel double-wishbone suspension, this specimen offers surgical turn-in and impeccable handling. All factory VIN tags are intact, confirming a pristine, unmodified example with zero mechanical compromise or cosmetic wear. A true turn-key enthusiast piece.",
