      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she's a total showstopper! This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered it since day one. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
